# Data — raw and processed live outside version control.
# Sackmann data is NOT tracked as git submodules: the upstream repos
# (github.com/JeffSackmann/tennis_atp · tennis_wta) now 404, and an
# unreachable submodule remote breaks the HF Space build checkout
# (job fails before Docker even runs). data/raw/ is populated locally
# (clone the Sackmann mirrors there); production data comes from the
# companion HF Dataset, not these dirs. See docs/phases.md Phase 8.
data/raw/*
data/processed/*
!data/raw/.gitkeep
!data/processed/.gitkeep

# Model artifacts (root-level only — src/tennis_predictor/models/ is the Python package)
/models/

# DuckDB snapshots pulled for HF bootstrap (never commit the 1.3 GB DB)
*.duckdb
*.duckdb.wal

# Notebooks: tracked, but outputs stripped by pre-commit
# (no ignore needed; nbstripout handles it)

# IDE / editor
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
.DS_Store

# Claude Code — per-machine permission state, not shared
.claude/settings.local.json

# Personal study materials — kept locally, not part of the public repo
docs/tutorials/
tennis_predictor_bootstrap_prompt.md
# Notebooks prefixed with `_` are private experimentation scratchpads
notebooks/_*.ipynb

